# ── Example sync flow ──────────────────────────────────

example: {
  label: |md
    **Example: Opus -> Sablier project sync**

    1. User creates project "Acme" in Opus
    2. Opus emits `{app: "opus", object: "project", action: "created", facile_id: "fac_xyz"}`
    3. Nook persists event in queue
    4. Router checks registry: Sablier registered for "project" events
    5. Nook delivers to `POST sablier.internal/webhooks/nook`
    6. Sablier creates mirror project, stores `facile_id: "fac_xyz"`
    7. Event logged — Perception observes for analytics
  |
  shape: page
  near: bottom-center
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#bdbdbd"
  style.border-radius: 8
  style.font-size: 13
}
